-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
LOCAL DEVELOPMENT & TESTING ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
This file is a template for the environment variables needed to run this
project locally. Copy this file to a new file named .env and fill in your
local configuration values. The .env file is ignored by Git and should
NOT be committed to the repository.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
--- Redis Configuration ---
Used for caching and session storage in development.
REDIS_HOST=localhost
REDIS_PORT=6379

--- PostgreSQL Database Configuration ---
These are credentials for your LOCAL PostgreSQL instance.
Do NOT use production credentials here.
DATABASE_NAME=test_db
DATABASE_USER=test_user
DATABASE_PASSWORD=test_pass
WRITER_DB_HOST=localhost
READER_DB_HOST=localhost
DATABASE_PORT=5432